<h1 style="font-size:50px;text-align:center;">NEWS</h1>
<p>News is information about recent events, developments, or significant occurrences that is shared through various media channels to inform the public. Typically, news covers a wide range of topics, including politics, business, culture, science, health, and sports, and is presented through sources like newspapers, television, radio, websites, and social media. News is often selected for its relevance, impact, proximity, timeliness, or interest to a particular audience.</p>
<a style="font-size:20px;" href="https://www.google.com/">Read more</a>
